Package: pkgmaker
Type: Package
Title: Package development utilities
Version: 0.1
Date: 2012-05-23
Author: Renaud Gaujoux
Maintainer: Renaud Gaujoux <renaud@cbio.uct.ac.za>
Description: This package provides some low-level utilities to use for package
    development.
    It is still under heavy development and changes in the interface are more
    than likely.
License: GPL (>=2)
URL: http://pkgmaker.r-forge.r-project.org
LazyLoad: yes
